Yeah it is adrienne

42
00:02:42,660 --> 00:02:44,780
Why is it so important to research this really?

43
00:02:45,180 --> 00:02:47,180
It is a matter of democracy.

44
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,700
These closed arenas, they are becoming more and more.

45
00:02:50,180 --> 00:02:52,620
And that means that more political issues

46
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:56,500
Become a reality in these closed rooms.

47
00:02:57,140 --> 00:03:00,580
It is so effective to do that way

48
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,680
Instead of doing something very public.

49
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:05,180
But it is not so good for us who are citizens.

50
00:03:05,820 --> 00:03:09,940
Because we need to know what is happening and we may need to discuss

51
00:03:10,220 --> 00:03:11,880
What this development means.

52
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:17,940
For this to be possible, we need to have stable and reliable knowledge

53
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:20,240
about that change.

54
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,400
So, we need research.

55
